latestIgtvVideos.title: Stay with @oyorooms.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
My trip to the Pink City was nothing more than a dream which I experienced with open eyes. To experience the taste of this bustling city, “Jaipur”, I booked my stay at @oyorooms .

From being known for its beautiful forts and palaces, Jaipur is also known for its hospitality, which is why it is called the Pink City as pink signifies hospitality. Apart from being the largest city of the Indian state of Rajasthan, it is also a very popular tourist destination in India with some heart throbbing palaces, forts and museums like Amer Fort, Jal Mahal & Albert Hall Museum

I booked myself at 5 by OYO - Metropolitan, which was a 5-star hotel, centrally located property in C-scheme Jaipur. I booked a suite room with a/c, which was very hygienic and spacious.

I was very impressed with all the kinds of precautions they were taking to safeguard their customers and also to respect the Nationwide covid protocols. Not only this, their check-in timings are pretty flexible so you don’t have to worry even if you’re jet lagging.

Apart from the hotel, the people & tour guides are very helpful and sweet but since the city is known for its tourism, some guides might befool you therefore, be smart before spending any penny.

To Unlock with my first trip to Jaipur w/ @oyorooms and relish the taste of culture, go through this link and check out our captivating property at “https://www.oyorooms.com/79251/“.
A regal affair that you don't want to miss, apply coupon code “OYOUNLOCK” to get some great offers.

#RajasthanTourism #OyoRooms #SBYE #LeisureStays #UnLockwithOyo
